### EdgeHardware Controller (internal Web API)
### Base URL is the Haus application server

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv HAUS_BASE_URL}}

### Get latest snapshots for all edge nodes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/edgehardware
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get recent events (default limit 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/edgehardware/events
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get recent events with custom limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/edgehardware/events?limit=50
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}
